S'imagina egna pagina d'internet fetg lùnga cun blearas secziùns (ina specificaziùn HTML sen egna pagina). Sch'igl utilisader dumonda egna tschearta part (p.ex. page.html#section7) , co savess igl easser, sch'igl server-web streams igl amprem questa part a suainter las ulteriuras parts?
Successiun digl stream:
1. Cumenzament digl document HTML fin <body>
2. HTML par la part 7
3. HTML per las secziuns 1, 2, 3 a.a.a.
Alura procurass igl browser ca las parts 1 antocen 6 *davart* la part 7 vignian mussas sen la pagina d'internet.
Fa quegl sen? Fuss quegl egn agid?
La part cun in link (#section7) duai vegnir renderida aschi speart sco pussevel, sainza puspe stuer implementar elemaints cun JavaScript. Jou savess semplameing ver egn document HTML extra, mo las parts ca vignan liadas ston vagnir renderadas aschi speart sco pussevel. Cun HTML duess quegl funcziunar.
Igl cuntegn savess vagnir transmess ascheia, ad alura stuess igl browser meter tut igls <contents> an la <div>.
< div ig = sec1></div>
< div id= sec2></div>
etc.
< div ig = sec7>section 7...</div>
< cuntents for=sec1>section 1...</contents>
< cuntents for=sec2>section 2...</contents>
etc.
Igl vegn betga transmess an la suczessiùn, mo igl browser mettia anzemel igl document HTML ascheia, sco sch'igl fiss vagnieu transmess an la suczessiùn.
